rows.label: tlk4170042104_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, Superbia... Your indomitable
flames... Your singular will, sharp as
a spearpoint...

rows.label: tlk4170042104_msg0002
rows.name:
I was writing poetry about Gula
until some soldiers ordered me instead
to write about the glory of Superbia...

rows.label: tlk4170042104_msg0003
rows.name:
They said they'd pay me if they
liked it, so I'm putting everything
I've got into it!
